name: Haneul
description:
Haneul is one lovely and cheerful highschool girl, she likes to travel around to various places while wearing her modern hanbok.
Hanbok 한복 is a traditional Korean clothes. The term "hanbok" literally means Korean clothing. 
Hanbok itself hanbok was used to distinguish Korean clothing from Japanese traditional clothing and Western clothing. And usually used for for formal or semi-formal occasions and events such as festivals, celebrations, and ceremonies.
